@page "/tables"

<PageTitle>表格 (Tables) - Bootstrap 展示</PageTitle>

<h2>📊 表格 (Tables)</h2>
<p class="lead">表格变体：基础、条纹、悬停、带边框、无边框、响应式、彩色及紧凑型。</p>

<h5 class="mt-4">基础与条纹 (Basic & Striped)</h5>
<div class="table-responsive mb-4">
    <table class="table table-striped">
        <thead class="table-dark">
            <tr><th>#</th><th>姓名 (Name)</th><th>角色 (Role)</th><th>状态 (Status)</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            <tr><td>1</td><td>张三</td><td>开发者</td><td><span class="badge bg-success">在线</span></td></tr>
            <tr><td>2</td><td>李四</td><td>设计师</td><td><span class="badge bg-warning">离开</span></td></tr>
            <tr><td>3</td><td>王五</td><td>经理</td><td><span class="badge bg-success">在线</span></td></tr>
            <tr><td>4</td><td>赵六</td><td>测试</td><td><span class="badge bg-danger">离线</span></td></tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>
</div>

<h5>悬停与带边框 (Hover & Bordered)</h5>
<div class="table-responsive mb-4">
    <table class="table table-hover table-bordered">
        <thead class="table-primary">
            <tr><th>#</th><th>产品 (Product)</th><th>价格 (Price)</th><th>库存 (Stock)</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            <tr><td>1</td><td>小工具 A</td><td>¥99.99</td><td>142</td></tr>
            <tr><td>2</td><td>小配件 B</td><td>¥249.99</td><td>87</td></tr>
            <tr><td>3</td><td>小零件 C</td><td>¥149.99</td><td>0</td></tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>
</div>

<h5>紧凑与无边框 (Small & Borderless)</h5>
<div class="table-responsive mb-4">
    <table class="table table-sm table-borderless">
        <thead><tr><th>#</th><th>物品 (Item)</th><th>数量 (Qty)</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
            <tr><td>1</td><td>苹果</td><td>5</td></tr>
            <tr><td>2</td><td>橘子</td><td>3</td></tr>
            <tr><td>3</td><td>香蕉</td><td>8</td></tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>
</div>

<h5>情景行 (Contextual Rows)</h5>
<div class="table-responsive mb-4">
    <table class="table">
        <thead><tr><th>类名 (Class)</th><th>效果 (Effect)</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
            <tr class="table-active"><td>.table-active</td><td>活跃行高亮</td></tr>
            <tr class="table-primary"><td>.table-primary</td><td>主要行高亮</td></tr>
            <tr class="table-success"><td>.table-success</td><td>成功行高亮</td></tr>
            <tr class="table-danger"><td>.table-danger</td><td>危险行高亮</td></tr>
            <tr class="table-warning"><td>.table-warning</td><td>警告行高亮</td></tr>
            <tr class="table-info"><td>.table-info</td><td>信息行高亮</td></tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>
</div>

<h5>响应式表格（小屏幕上水平滚动）(Responsive Table)</h5>
<div class="table-responsive">
    <table class="table table-striped">
        <thead><tr><th>#</th><th>列 A</th><th>列 B</th><th>列 C</th><th>列 D</th><th>列 E</th><th>列 F</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
            <tr><td>1</td><td>数据</td><td>数据</td><td>数据</td><td>数据</td><td>数据</td><td>数据</td></tr>
            <tr><td>2</td><td>数据</td><td>数据</td><td>数据</td><td>数据</td><td>数据</td><td>数据</td></tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>
</div>
